        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[台湾公布海上监控山东舰画面]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/08/E58FB0E6B9BEE59BBDE998B2E983A8EFBC91_1.png?VersionId=VPCnlgCXhTKzCk8eRhu8__qdi7pjpnbl&amp;itok=QEx_VLIt" title="台湾公布海军监控大陆山东舰的画面。（台湾国防部）" alt="台湾公布海军监控大陆山东舰的画面。（台湾国防部）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/08/E58FB0E6B9BEE59BBDE998B2E983A8EFBC91_1.png?VersionId=VPCnlgCXhTKzCk8eRhu8__qdi7pjpnbl&amp;itok=QEx_VLIt" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
